title: October 14, 2015 - Tenant safety blitz starts October 19 (City of Guelph)
text: ( Source : City of Guelph ) Guelph, Ontario , October 14 , 2015 - The City of Guelph , in partnership with the Guelph Fire Department and University of Guelph Off-Campus Living office, is carrying out a tenant safety blitz from October 19 to 23,
